(6, 1, 1, 1, 1, 'Picture on the CV? Yes or No?', 'picture-on-the-cv?-yes-or-no?', '<p><em>The goal is to get you to the interview......</em></p>', '<p>A question I keep getting from clients is, if it advisable or beneficial to have a picture on your CV?<br />\n<br />\nMy take: I&#39;m actually torn on this topic. Just like your nationality, marital status, gender or age, photos should NOT be added to the resume for 2 reasons;<br />\n1. It&#39;s unnecessary.<br />\n2. Discrimination.<br />\n<br />\nThen, on the other side, we have become more visual in our communication. We are able to match faces to the names.<br />\n<br />\nThe goal is to get you to the interview. So without overthinking it, what I advise my clients is that we&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=revamp&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A6789867258672893952\">#revamp</a>&nbsp;the resumes without the pictures but ensure that the socials are well updated with a professional shot and a showcase of portfolios.<br />\n<br />\nSites like&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=linkedin&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A6789867258672893952\">#Linkedin</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/feed/hashtag/?keywords=staffscout&amp;highlightedUpdateUrns=urn%3Ali%3Aactivity%3A6789867258672893952\">#StaffScout</a>&nbsp;are great sites to showcase yourself adequately.</p>', 1, '[]', '2021-04-26 10:20:09', '2021-04-26 10:20:09', NULL),
